==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unshackle
<hw>Un*shac"kle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>shackle</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from shackles
or bonds; to set free from restraint; to unfetter.</def>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unshakable</ent>⟦br⟧
